t rendering errors (skybox goes pink for a frame or two).The 100 m/s max ship speed in vanilla is painfully slow at times, I've heard there are mods but I am a vanilla game player by trade. Even 200 or 250 m/s would make the game feel like hyper speed if you're used to the 100 m/s.Bugs. I've encountered some. Heard of many more. Wolves chewing through heavy metal armor. Really?I recommend if you want to play space Minecraft but with better creative production systems and the ability to build whatever you want and it will fly. 8/10 would crash land on moon again."
