 with the vacuum at very low speeds or 0 speed, ...edit after big multiplayer and graphics update (Dec 2016):graphics now look very nice, but need even more resouces. Its still buggy as hell (except multiplayer bugs, they were reduced by about 80%)(If I find an issue fixed, i will remove it from the list as soon as i notice)"
