ully functioning pistons, elevators and alot more.Yes the game is in alpha, but it doesnt feel like it. Theres so much to do! And there are only a very small amount of bugs, the game is almost flawless at such early stages.I would recommend space engineers to anyone, creative minds or not, you'll find something to do in this game and there will be so much more to come. The dev's are updating with new content, fixes, modes weekly!May the force be with you."
