,Recommended,244850,8747707,"Posted: 17 January, 2014",all,GalaxyHiker,"Definitely a worthwhile buy, if only to see where the game goes. Content updates are frequent and massive, and the game feels like it's MOVING at a rapid pace toward some amazing conclusion. Of course, things that are being added are things that you'd expect to be present in a non-Alpha game, but seeing them go in before your eyes makes you feel like the developers are doing good work.Physics are good (if wonky at times), momentum seems to run like it should. If you're into the more realistic flight model there are keys to toggle inertial dampers, but the game defaults to the much simpler and easier-to-learn basic flight scheme.If you want an idea of what people can DO with this game, check its Workshop page. The creations are staggering.The last update added a collision-model editor to the modkit, which opens up whole new possibilities for modification. MULTIPLAYER IS NOW A THING. So yes.Buy this game."
