ips via Workshop.This goes on to two other things i have nearly forgot to mention. Bored of simple Survival or playing alone? You can acces the Missionstab that was implemented a few updates ago to play Missions by the devs itself or by modders. Even you could make one yourself very easily. You dont even have to know how to mod since the thing you need is only one: The game. And as you know i wrote something about playing with your friends. And i know most of you dont just wanna by a server. That is why this game has a cooptional feature built in. This game lets you open your world to the public or to your Steamfriends. This allows you to play with others freely as long as you are online or the host if you have joined.And now its already time to end this review. Would i recommend this game? Oh hell yes.There might be bugs and such but hey the game is still in development and its worth the price already."
