,Recommended,244850,33093080,Posted: 1 July,all,Liger_XT5,"I don't much I can say that many other, positive, reviewers haven't said.I will say this. Remember it's a game in beta. There are weekly updates.Save frequently, every 5-10 minutes. If the game pauses for saving more often than you like, increase the time, or disable auto-saving, and save manually.Bonus/Brownie points: Have a program keeping the last few minutes of game activity on screen recorded. Similar to Xbox's ""Record That"" function. You will have funny moments you'd want to save for later, or even share. Youcoulduse Windows 10 game recorder. However I recommend others such as Nvidia's Game Experience, OBS Studio, and I think X Split has it too."
